    <item>
      <title>Ano ang Ibig Sabihin ng Maharlika?</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/tl/history/meanings-maharlika/</link>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 Nov 2023 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/tl/history/meanings-maharlika/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Ang Maharlika ang pangalan ng pre-colonial na confederation na nakabase sa &lt;strong&gt;Maynila&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Ang ibig sabihin ng &lt;em&gt;maha&lt;/em&gt; ay malaki kagaya ng &lt;em&gt;Maha&lt;/em&gt;rashtra at &lt;em&gt;Maha&lt;/em&gt;bharata.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;May dagdag ito na &lt;code&gt;r&lt;/code&gt; kapag kinakabit sa ibang salita.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Ang ibig sabihin ng &lt;em&gt;lika&lt;/em&gt; ay:&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
